!Sorry if anything is mis-spelled!
Some important points to  be  followed
1. In ApplyURI field replace username and passsword with the login credentials to your Mongo Atlas
2. The given program creates two different collections one for asset and one for details.
3. The details is supposed to carry details of individuals and asset contains info of related asset info
4. The eid(employee id) is used as primary key and relates both the collections. The lid(asset id) can be used as foreign key for future enhancements if needed.

!!! If you're wondering what a collection is, it is a table as we say in RDBMS !!!
$%& MongoDB uses bson to utilize values, some common formats are: bson.M(for mapping), bson.A(for array), bson.D(no filter values). $%& 
